FOUR RARE PHOTOGRAPHS OF THE KINGS FAISAL II OF IRAQ AND SAUD BIN ABD AL-AZIZ, WITH SOME ROYALS AND POLITICIANS, 1950s
Two photos of the former King of Iraq, Faisal II bin, King Ghazi bin Faisal I bin al Hussain with King Saud bin Abd Al-Aziz, Abd al-llah bin Ali served as regent for Prince Faisal II before he became king of Iraq and Nuri al-said former prime minister of Iraq meeting Mostaffa el-Nahas and Egyptian politician. 

Two photographs of King Faisal II at a young age, one with his guards having an afternoon rest at school and the one together with  one of his sisters.

7 by 11 cm.

13 by 18 cm.
